### Package Dependency Rules
- **`@beings/core`**: Must have ZERO framework dependencies. Contains the core logic for the "Slow Track".
- **`@beings/react`**: Depends only on `@beings/core` and the React ecosystem.
- **`@beings/ui`**: Purely presentational; receives all state via props.
- **`@beings/app`**: The integration layer that consumes all other packages.
